</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【unwire TV】【實試】 疫苗通行證實試，掃瞄針卡程序 + 注意事項</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/16/unwire-tv-vaccine-pass/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=unwire-tv-vaccine-pass</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[nickman]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 16 Feb 2022 13:00:20 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[unwire TV]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1086563</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>宜家愈黎愈多地方要 scan 安心出行，遲啲仲要掃描埋針卡，一齊睇一睇成個流程啦&#8230;&#8230; &#038; [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>宜家愈黎愈多地方要 scan 安心出行，遲啲仲要掃描埋針卡，一齊睇一睇成個流程啦&#8230;&#8230;<br />&nbsp;<br />#安心出行 #疫苗通行證 #首階段<br />&nbsp;<br /><iframe loading="lazy" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=314&#038;href=https%3A%2F%2Fbusiness.facebook.com%2Funwirehk%2Fvideos%2F992559028021311%2F&#038;show_text=false&#038;width=560&#038;t=0" width="560" height="314" style="border:none;overflow:hidden" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="true" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowFullScreen="true"></iframe></p></p><div class="feedflare">
